4 Section 2200. A. There is hereby created recreated, to
5 continue until June 1, 2026, the Oklahoma Organized Retail Crime
6 Task Force until December 31, 2024. The purpose of the task force
7 shall be to provide the Legislature and the Governor with
8 information on organized retail crime and the advantages and
9 drawbacks of instituting various countermeasures to counter losses
10 from retail theft in the state.
